{"tid":1915810,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"3月9號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-03-08T13:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T00:43:24.000Z","uid":292499,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9441f63527168cb0aa48c72f6a8b911c85849b63","tid":1915810,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 3 月 9 日 星期一】<br />\n<br />\n►--- 09:30 am ---◄ <br />\n🏛屯門裁判法院 3 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️#張潔宜署理主任裁判官<br />\n👤陳(27)（#0730天水圍 刑事毀壞、普通襲擊:涉損壞行人隧道牆壁並襲擊休班警X）<br />\n👤劉(17)🛑<strong>已還押5天</strong>（#20200212香港仔 縱火:中銀櫃員機）<br />\n👥鄧,荷蘭藉手足(31-42)🛑<strong>已還押5天</strong>（#20200229旺角 縱火:垃圾桶）<br />\n<br />\n＊另有新案件，未知幾號庭提堂，請留意明天 法庭文字直播 資訊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">＊3月7號深夜至8號凌晨多區爆門拘捕既手足幾大機會天日09:30/14:30提堂，由於天日只會有屯門裁判法院開，所以好高機會都係係屯門提堂，天日屯門裁判法院要人呀</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3ae0418f15cb820a9425d9bfa4d5fcac9b9193","tid":1915810,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=9f81d223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"f5ff8c8e867ce159efa8a09811fb770125248b62","tid":1915810,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=6365346c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=1211ff02\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"391962b38c31dba2baf6fb6cf45b3eb8953141f7","tid":1915810,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyTwKQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyTwKQq.jpg&h=26284547&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3986d3ef43b9a356ea487d17bc29be857809bbae","tid":1915810,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:02:53.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"4ccbb064a1de29b5bd8116525ac635dbe66c0fa6","tid":1915810,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n屯門裁判法院交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界</strong><br />\n荃灣區：60M [屯門公園] (推薦), 68A [屯門大會堂]<br />\n青衣：68A [屯門大會堂]<br />\n沙田區：263 [屯門公園]<br />\n北區：261 [屯門官立中學]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n油尖旺區：60X [屯門市中心], 63X [屯門大會堂], 260X [屯門市廣場] (推薦)<br />\n深水埗區：60X [屯門市中心], 63X [屯門大會堂], 58X [屯門市廣場]<br />\n九龍城區：61X [屯門市中心]<br />\n觀塘區：62X, 259D [屯門市中心]<br />\n黃大仙區：62X, 259D [屯門市中心]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中西區：960 [屯門市廣場] ,961 [屯門公園]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"649dfae1afa8e7990068f87bdc5e0733c967961b","tid":1915810,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6326e766f6682a5dad067f964164dd20f8e24a","tid":1915810,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1267f8dbbc23878c69c29b6836b8dcbc3e36e2b","tid":1915810,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41c959c8be1dd5a09f515b467e0d47f658db6cd","tid":1915810,"uid":253405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e027d0cc04310d23deb9b94e31f402185d206e","tid":1915810,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2baacc48c7486544906e33e49cc3cb815e6ab22","tid":1915810,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3e3123ad7f1199ea416891d40d12d9ebaff0d4",